Page_0: "New brethren are encouraged to use extreme caution whilst using the Builder's tools. Follow thine instructions carefully to maketh the finest of instruments:

1. Placeth thy mold onto the rest
2. Pull the Mold Lever to seal the lock in place
3. Pull the Cauldron Lever to begin the smelting process
4. Await the Builder's iron to pour, lest thy tool may be inadequate
5. Only when the Cauldron Lever resets shouldst thy then pull the Mold Lever again to claim thy tools"